{"tid":1519163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經聽過太多性侵案例，要諗計保護好自己！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-30T13:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T20:39:32.000Z","uid":110613,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"49c612ac9f54c06a9a17afbca904ac0f0f93b4b4","tid":1519163,"uid":110613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"有太多太多人被狗性侵，甚至更傳有少女被輪姦<br />\n雖然未有真FC出現，但諗一下都覺得太嬲啦！！！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更嬲既係連追究都追究唔到<br />\n狗屋無CCTV，呢d事發生左一次就會有第二次<br />\nd狗成日出強姦犯唔少見，未捉到既有幾多個？！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔想再講氣憤說話，求大家諗下計點樣保護好自己</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防強姦</span><br />\n上網搵\b防強姦既我搵到呢d<br />\n有冇人知道香港可以係邊購入？！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/un1SckE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fun1SckE.png&h=59b11acd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UgJM1d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUgJM1d1.png&h=f05aa404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n83AUy2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn83AUy2.png&h=82bb1674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HiuDSkJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHiuDSkJ.png&h=3d95e529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">錄音做證供</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">律政司及保安局：秘密錄音並非絕對不可作為呈堂證據</span><br />\n//（一）在刑事審訊中，法庭有酌情權決定證據的可接納性，主要考慮因素包括證案價值；會否造成偏見；進行錄音人士的身份、理由與動機；對涉案公職人員的指控；以及尋求將錄音呈堂的法律程序的性質等。根據案例，秘密錄音並非絕對不可作為呈堂證據。<br />\n<br />\n  就紀律研訊而言，也沒有普遍的原則規定所有秘密錄音均不能被接納作為證據。決策局或部門須考慮該錄音能否證明相關事實，及在研訊中接納該錄音為證據是否公平公正。過程中需要根據個別情況作出判斷，不能一概而論。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201706/14/P2017061400479.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201706%2F14%2FP2017061400479.htm&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=80520be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201706/14/P2017061400479.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n因為狗屋會搜身，有冇高手知會唔會有極細型同貼身既錄音筆可以錄低證據？"},{"pid":"fc0727b0b21efb53218361148d1926c6e7538c1f","tid":1519163,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qw3QgZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQw3QgZA.jpg&h=c3ca146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=527aedeb\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=3b7ab847\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=cc7a5582\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"d4dc6de8289395c948ab606533d16dab0e73f1f3","tid":1519163,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCk